\\\"2\\\"], \\\"+\\\", \\\"y\\\"}], \\\"]\\\"}], \\\"\[Equal]\\\", \
\\\"0\\\"}]}], \\\",\\\", RowBox[{\\\"WorkingPrecision\\\", \\\"\[Rule]\\\", \
